{"data":[{"date":"22:31 23/06","title":"\u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (KT): Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 s\u1ed1ng d\u1eady t\u1eeb c\u00f5i ch\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/ket-qua-duc-vs-thuy-dien.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda t\u1eed (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc), Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n gh\u00ea g\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \"c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\" trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</h2><h2>Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda t\u1eed (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc), Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n gh\u00ea g\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \"c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\" trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</h2>\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-duc-vs-thuy-dien-463-189371.html\" target=\"_blank\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110\u1ee8C VS TH\u1ee4Y \u0110I\u1ec2N</span><br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"509","checkdouble":"189371"},{"date":"23:19 23/06","title":"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea3ng G g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\u2026 bay v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc. Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n bi\u1ec3u d\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc Phi?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video data-dashjs-player=\"\" src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/201806/273294/stream.mpd\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n1. B\u1ec9 t\u1ed5ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Tunisia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoberto Martinez c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 c\u00e1ch Tunisia t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea7ng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1ed5 s\u1edf ra sao trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, v\u1eady n\u00ean HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u0169 b\u00e3o h\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia C\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia C\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: C\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1edbm</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nCh\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Kevin De Bruyne \u00e1n ng\u1eef tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ed9 tam v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 n\u00ean nh\u1edb b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng, trong khi m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5 Axel Witsel c\u00f9ng wing-back hai c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u00e2ng cao d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng co c\u1ee5m v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-bi-vs-tunisia-463-189356.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia</span>.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTam t\u1ea5u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Romelu Lukaku, Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Dries Mertens \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Tunisia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ecb qu\u1ea7n th\u1ea3o v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1, v\u1edbi then ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Hazard gi\u00fap mang v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty ngay \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1edbm, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc Phi ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n t\u1eeb trong tr\u1ee9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc. 84 ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, B\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">2. B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi &ldquo;hot trend&rdquo; c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKi\u1ebfm t\u00ecm \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o \u0111i m\u00f2 kim \u0111\u00e1y b\u1ec3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1edf h\u1eefu d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c t\u1ef1a nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhan hi\u1ebfm khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n m\u00e0 Tunisia hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin khai th\u00e1c, v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a d\u00e1m nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B, C&hellip; \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ho\u1eb7c xoay chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i khi kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi 5-2 Tunisia\" title=\"B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/231459-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: B\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ec3 b\u00e0n thua &ldquo;kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n&rdquo; ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 an b\u00e0i, tuy\u1ec3n Anh n\u00ean xem x\u00e9t ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, Tunisia ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n: \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t &ndash; t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh &ndash; \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u. So v\u1edbi c\u1ea5p CLB th\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf World Cup, tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ee9u c\u00e1nh cho s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00f3i l\u00ean xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi. B\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t cho Anh, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00f2ng knock-out trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3. Hazard x\u1ee9ng danh th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng \u00edt tranh c\u00e3i n\u1ed5 ra xoay quanh t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng trao cho Hazard tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 khi b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ebfn, c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard Bi vs Tunisia\" title=\"Hazard B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: Hazard ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Vincent Kompany v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Hazard \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o m\u1ecdi nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn sai l\u1ea7m v\u1ec1 anh. Ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch s\u1ef1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Lukaku trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u, k\u00e9o theo 45 ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man Utd v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Panama.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Tunisia, vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Hazard c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t, \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t De Bruyne kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thua k\u00e9m c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u00f9i s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng ni\u00ean. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecf con khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc b\u1eb1ng qu\u1ea3 penalty &ldquo;t\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfm t\u1ef1 \u0103n&rdquo;, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n cho c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Lukaku.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Hazard c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi pha x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1eeba th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng. 21 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t kho\u00e1c \u00e1o B\u1ec9, Hazard in d\u1ea5u gi\u1ea7y trong 23 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ghi 11 v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 12.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">4. C\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh ti\u1ec5n Tunisia v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane, hai t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u00edt \u1ecfi m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Tunisia ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ch\u00e2u Phi x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng cao nh\u1ea5t FIFA.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2u ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh Tam S\u01b0, ngay c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e1t m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i h\u1ed9t v\u1edbi Tunisia trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018. V\u1eady n\u00ean d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng B\u1ec9 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia C\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia C\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia: C\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ngu\u1ed3n c\u01a1n n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t ch\u1ec9 sau 5 ph\u00fat b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, khi c\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng c\u1ea9u th\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Syam Ben Youssef mang v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hazard th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Tunisia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u01a1i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n oan u\u1ed5ng b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec3m ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean v\u1ea1ch 16m50.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00c2u c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a s\u1ee9c \u00e9p ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u1ec9 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o ra v\u00e0 Tunisia \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea1i B\u00e0ng v\u00f9ng Carthage \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd d\u00e2ng cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd c\u00f3 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 xi\u00ean th\u00eam 4 nh\u00e1t dao k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Anh \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee5c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 cho nhau \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c xa v\u00e0 Panama c\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. Sau chi\u1ec1u mai theo gi\u1edd Nga, b\u1ea3ng G s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c an b\u00e0i hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 m\u00e1y bay v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Bi 5-2 Tunisia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Thong-ke-Bi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-bi-vs-tunisia-463-189356.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nhan-dinh-bi-vs-tunisia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-tunisia-vs-bi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-bi-vs-tunisia-463-189356.html\">B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia (KT): Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1o m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Spartak</span><br>\r\nHai ng\u00f4i sao thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Hazard vs Lukaku thay nhau l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"508","checkdouble":"189373"},{"date":"00:06 24/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u00fat bay \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ra kh\u1ecfi World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/nguoi-thuy-dien-tuyen-bo-sut-bay-dkvd-duc-ra-khoi-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda t\u1eed (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc), Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n gh\u00ea g\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \"c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\" trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</h2><em><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh video (B\u1ea2N QUY\u1ec0N VTV)</span></strong></em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c: Reus (48'), Kroos (90'+5)<br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: Toivonen (32')<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c: Manuel Neuer; Joshua Kimmich, Antonio Rudiger, Jerome Boateng,  Jonas Hector; Sebastian Rudy, Toni Kroos; Marco Reus, Thomas Muller,  Julian Draxler; Timo Werner. <br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: Robin Olsen; Mikael Lustig, Victor Lindelof, Andreas  Granqvist, Ludwig Augustinsson; Viktor Claesson, Sebastian Larsson,  Albin Ekdal, Emil Forsberg; Ola Toivonen, Marcus Berg. <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"507","checkdouble":"189374"},{"date":"00:29 24/06","title":"Tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ed9n b\u1ec1 \u00e2u lo, v\u1ee5 Leroy Sane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u01a1i l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/4/tuyen-duc-bon-be-au-lo-vu-leroy-sane-duoc-khoi-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Lothar Matthaus v\u00e0 Michael Ballack \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ng\u1ea7m ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ng\u00f4i sao Man City c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u s\u1ed1c n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. \u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u01a1i l\u1ea1i</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ee5 Leroy Sane b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ee5 Leroy Sane b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/tuyen-duc-bon-be-au-lo-vu-leroy-sane-duoc-khoi-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leroy Sane b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u01a1n c\u1ea3 v\u1ee5 Radja Nainggolan v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, vi\u1ec7c Leroy Sane kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, bao g\u1ed3m b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t n\u0103m ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man City v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng lao \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb hay nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00e2u lo b\u1ed9n b\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf Mannschaft, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng: \u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn Mexico v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn Leroy Sane v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 hi\u1ec3u l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c, Michael Ballack c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201cJoachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 t\u1ea5n \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Leroy Sane, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho ch\u00fang ta.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cChuy\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 l\u00fd khi Leroy Sane m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f9ng Man City. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c sao? T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u1eeb phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn tri\u1ebft l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u1eafm r\u00f5 v\u00e0 anh ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecfi ch\u00ednh Loew th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-duc-vs-thuy-dien-463-189371.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/link-xem-duc-vs-thuy-dien.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-duc-vs-thuy-dien-463-189371.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 01h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 01h00 \u0111\u00eam...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"506","checkdouble":"189375"},{"date":"01:41 24/06","title":"T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-2 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/clip-ban-thang-han-quoc-vs-mexico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Mexico ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1e