color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda t\u1eed (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc), Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n gh\u00ea g\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \"c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\" trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</h2><em><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh video (B\u1ea2N QUY\u1ec0N VTV)</span></strong></em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c: Reus (48'), Kroos (90'+5)<br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: Toivonen (32')<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c: Manuel Neuer; Joshua Kimmich, Antonio Rudiger, Jerome Boateng,  Jonas Hector; Sebastian Rudy, Toni Kroos; Marco Reus, Thomas Muller,  Julian Draxler; Timo Werner. <br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: Robin Olsen; Mikael Lustig, Victor Lindelof, Andreas  Granqvist, Ludwig Augustinsson; Viktor Claesson, Sebastian Larsson,  Albin Ekdal, Emil Forsberg; Ola Toivonen, Marcus Berg. <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"504","checkdouble":"189377"},{"date":"03:06 24/06","title":"B\u1ec9 thi\u1ec7t qu\u00e2n nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng cho \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/bi-thiet-quan-nghiem-trong-cho-dai-chien-voi-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia, HLV Roberto Martinez ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 hai ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Anh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bi-vs-tunisia-421-189357.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia</span> l\u00e0m n\u00ean c\u01a1m m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u0169ng 99,99% \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard v\u00e0 Lukaku ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hazard v\u00e0 Lukaku ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/bi-thiet-quan-nghiem-trong-cho-dai-chien-voi-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard v\u00e0 Lukaku c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tin t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i k\u00e9m vui xoay quanh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 th\u00ec Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku, hai ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia, \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: \u201cHazard ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n, c\u00f2n Lukaku g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf m\u1eaft c\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng n\u00f3 trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u00e2y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m n\u00ean m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm thay c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra s\u00e2n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 xem x\u00e9t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn.\u201d \u2013 Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi\u1ec7t qu\u00e2n nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh Anh vs B\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G, khi Panama c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0 t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia-421-189373.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia-421-189373.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea3ng G g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"503","checkdouble":"189378"},{"date":"04:23 24/06","title":"San b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Lukaku n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/san-bang-thanh-tich-cua-ronaldo-lukaku-noi-gi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng G, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Romelu Lukaku ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nLukaku v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ed9i bom<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-bi-vs-tunisia-463-189356.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u1ebfp theo tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia</span>. 2 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard, Romelu Lukaku c\u00f9ng b\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ghi do c\u00f4ng Batshuayi gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0110T Anh ch\u01b0a thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man United \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f9ng Cris Ronaldo. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n&rdquo; &ndash; Lukaku cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac h\u01a1n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng cho th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lukaku ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia\" title=\"Lukaku B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/san-bang-thanh-tich-cua-ronaldo-lukaku-noi-gi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lukaku&nbsp;ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Tuy nhi\u00ean to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn lao. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ee9 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng th\u00f4i. Ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111em l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia, Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a anh ra ngh\u1ec9. Ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&rdquo; &ndash; Lukaku ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia. &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, ho\u1eb7c ng\u00e0y mai c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Anh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB, nh\u01b0ng ngay khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec m\u00e0u c\u1edd s\u1eafc \u00e1o qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia-421-189373.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia-421-189373.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea3ng G g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-sieu-ky-luc-sau-64-nam-421-189367.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/hazard-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-sieu-ky-luc-sau-64-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-sieu-ky-luc-sau-64-nam-421-189367.html\">Hazard gi\u00fap World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp si\u00eau k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau 64 n\u0103m</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 23/6, B\u1ec9 \u0111ang d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-tunisia-461-189366.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/hazard-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-sieu-ky-luc-sau-64-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-tunisia-461-189366.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 World Cup 2018 khi \u0111\u00e8 bep Tunisia. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Lukaku v\u00e0 Hazard m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"502","checkdouble":"189379"},{"date":"04:02 24/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \"\u0111au tim\" c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-dau-tim-cua-dt-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Low v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa mong manh c\u1ee7a Low<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111en Sami Khedira, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Toni Kroos trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Ilkay Gundogan hay Leon Goretzka, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 Sebastian Rudy &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Joachim Low d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Rudy ch\u01b0a t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0o th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong m\u1ed9t pha tranh ch\u1ea5p, anh \u0103n c\u1ea3 c\u00e1i g\u1ea7m gi\u00e0y c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Ilkay Gundogan m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ebfn ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, khi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n h\u1ecfng c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 sau 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n, khi Toivonen h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Neuer b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa l\u1ed1p b\u00f3ng tinh t\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Rudy r\u1eddi s\u00e2n t\u1eeb s\u1edbm l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/ger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rudy r\u1eddi s\u00e2n t\u1eeb s\u1edbm l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tan n\u00e1t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1-2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, do \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e2ng l\u00ean qu\u00e1 cao t\u00ecm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. Mats Hummels v\u00e0 Jerome Boateng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eafc v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n di\u1ec5n ra, Hummels \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf c\u1ed5 trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, d\u00f9 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong hi\u1ec7p 1, nh\u01b0ng \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p Boateng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n sau khi nh\u1eadn 2 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, khi\u1ebfn HLV Joachim Low c\u00e0ng th\u00eam \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf Antonio Rudiger trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ecf ra ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, khi b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Toivonen. D\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Boateng \u0103n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/boateng.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Boateng \u0103n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Marco Reus<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng Marco Reus trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n, \u0111em l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2. M\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0o hoa \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Borussia Dortmund.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi Julian Draxler \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ra ngh\u1ec9, nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Mario Gomez, Reus ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh &ndash; ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 ch\u00ednh trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft, khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng xu\u1ed1ng bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a chung cu\u1ed9c, ch\u00ednh Reus \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Toni Kroos t\u1ea1o ra si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. M\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Olsen b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfp theo, Marco Reus ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Joachim Low.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Reus v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/reu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: Reus v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1eb5n v\u00e9 m\u00e1y bay v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Mexico, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng sau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0111ang n\u1eafm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Mexico d\u00f9 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mexico. \u0110i\u1ec1u hay nh\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed1c 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n, chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e9t b\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Thong-so-Duc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/BXH-F.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-thuy-dien-461-189377.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/20180623T190726Z_938071254_RC1A5344D010_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPGERSWE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-thuy-dien-461-189377.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda t\u1eed (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc), Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n gh\u00ea g\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-duc-vs-thuy-dien-463-189371.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/ket-qua-duc-vs-thuy-dien.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-duc-vs-thuy-dien-463-189371.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (KT): Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 s\u1ed1ng d\u1eady t\u1eeb c\u00f5i ch\u1ebft</span><br>\r\nSau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda t\u1eed (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc), Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n gh\u00ea g\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-han-quoc-vs-mexico-461-189376.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/clip-ban-thang-han-quoc-vs-mexico.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-han-quoc-vs-mexico-461-189376.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1-2 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Mexico ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, qua \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edf toang c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"501","checkdouble":"189380"},{"date":"05:06 24/06","title":"Lukaku nh\u1eadn m\u01b0a l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb Hazard sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/lukaku-nhan-mua-loi-khen-tu-hazard-sau-tran-thang-tunisia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi c\u00f9ng nhau h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Tunisia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Eden Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i Lukaku v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.\r\n</h2><h2>Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i Lukaku<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Panama v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0110T B\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Tunisia 5-2. Trong \u0111\u00f3, song s\u00e1t Lukaku &ndash; Hazard g\u00f3p 4/5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, B\u1ec9 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng khi c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn Eden Hazard r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Romelu Lukaku &ndash; ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ngang b\u1eb1ng Cris Ronaldo c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i Lukaku: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 anh ch\u00e0ng n\u00e0y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng nhau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd. Khi Lukaku nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i Lukaku sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia\" title=\"Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/lukaku-nhan-mua-loi-khen-tu-hazard-sau-tran-thang-tunisia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i Lukaku sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, b\u1edfi \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, Tunisia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t v\u00e0 s\u1ebd lao l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1edf v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 trong nh\u1eefng pha di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng&rdquo; &ndash; Hazard k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Hazard ca ng\u1ee3i Lukaku, HLV Martinez c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh, Lukaku c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Witsel l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng: &ldquo;Rom \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ghi b\u00e0n r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Ngay c\u1ea3 trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, Lukaku c\u0169ng ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u00ean m\u1ed7i khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Lukaku lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao ghi b\u00e0n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/san-bang-thanh-tich-cua-ronaldo-lukaku-noi-gi-421-189379.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/san-bang-thanh-tich-cua-ronaldo-lukaku-noi-gi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/san-bang-thanh-tich-cua-ronaldo-lukaku-noi-gi-421-189379.html\">San b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Lukaku n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTrong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng G, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Romelu Lukaku ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia-421-189373.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia-421-189373.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea3ng G g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-tunisia-461-189366.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/hazard-giup-world-cup-2018-lap-sieu-ky-luc-sau-64-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-tunisia-461-189366.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 World Cup 2018 khi \u0111\u00e8 bep Tunisia. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Lukaku v\u00e0 Hazard m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"500","checkdouble":"189381"},{"date":"14:24 23/06","title":"Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal, Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/wilshere-roi-arsenal-mesut-ozil-da-cho-ngay-nay-tu-rat-lau-roi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jack Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Wilshere v\u1edbi Arsenal c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2018, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n song hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Mesut-Ozil-muon-ao-so-10-cua-Jack-Wilshere-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Emery \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, song anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ra s\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Jack Wilshere ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal-172-188988.html\" target=\"_blank\">Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal </span>theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thu v\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 xu n\u00e0o t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Southampton, West Ham v\u00e0 Everton \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Arsenal nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Wilshere \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh Emery \u0111\u00e3 sai khi kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ozil vui nh\u1ea5t khi Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb khi Mesut Ozil c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o m\u00e0 Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 \u0111eo t\u1eeb khi Robin van Persie chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MU v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil muon khoac ao so 10\" title=\"Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/wilshere-roi-arsenal-mesut-ozil-da-cho-ngay-nay-tu-rat-lau-roi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mesut Ozil mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 do\u00a0Wilshere b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 khi\u1ebfn Ozil ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 11. C\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Ozil l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 song \u00f4ng Wenger t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng Jack Wilshere, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi Wilshere ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00ec s\u1ed1 10 \u1edf Arsenal v\u1eabn b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng, \u00f4ng Wenger t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u00f9 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Ozil kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Arsenal th\u00ec Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u00e0y t\u1ecf \u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Theo Daily Mail, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafn v\u1edbi HLV Emery r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea5y l\u00e2u c\u1ee7a Ozil s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Ozil \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u00e1o m\u00e0 anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh \u1edf \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"499","checkdouble":"189348"},{"date":"14:38 23/06","title":"L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/7/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-mateo-kovacic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Spurs ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kovacic quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 14 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf hai m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Tottenham-muon-mua-Mateo-Kovacic-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 24, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Marca, HLV Lopetegui s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Kovacic m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/kovacic-muon-roi-real-180-189338.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Spurs ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-mateo-kovacic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Pochettino s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay Dembele \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU, AC Milan v\u00e0 PSG theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Dembele s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic t\u1eeb Real Madrid. HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Spurs l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKovacic gia nh\u1eadp Real t\u1eeb Inter v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e8 2015. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Los Blancos nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Spurs \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"498","checkdouble":"189349"},{"date":"14:38 23/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP SLNA 1-0 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (H2): Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/slna-vs-can-tho-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>