{ display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gabriel Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Brazil. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao PSG sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Costa Rica.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Neymar l\u00e0 ch\u00e0ng trai vui v\u1ebb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica. Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho. V\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau, Neymar \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho Selecao trong s\u1ef1 sung s\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c, si\u00eau sao Neymar b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng g\u1ee5c xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n kh\u00f3c th\u00fat th\u00edt khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem hoang mang. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n sau khi b\u1ecf d\u1edf m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/jesus-phat-bieu-ve-neymar-mit-uot-cua-dt-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng qua m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, Neymar chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Gabriel Jesus, anh tin r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNeymar \u1ed5n th\u00f4i. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u1ebb, anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai vui v\u1ebb\u201d, Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar. \u201cAnh \u1ea5y t\u1ecfa ra h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta, \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn Brazil. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Neymar m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u00e3y tr\u00e2n qu\u00fd v\u00e0 tin v\u00e0o ni\u1ec1m tin \u0111\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jesus mo ty so cho Brazil\" title=\"Jesus mo ty so cho Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/jesus-xem-nhe-danh-hieu-vua-pha-luoi-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Jesus ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Jesus kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 Firmino</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Neymar gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Jesus l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3. Anh lu\u00f4n trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ecb so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Roberto Firmino v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Jesus cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Firmino. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng khi m\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i cho \u0110TQG\u201d, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. \u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai ra s\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tite.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i, Firmino c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng, d\u00f9 Firmino c\u00f3 ra s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189317.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189317.html\">4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110T Brazil cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Costa Rica thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-brazil-vs-costa-rica-binh-luan-brazil-vs-costa-rica-421-189305.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/Coutinho-an-mung-sau-khi-ghi-ban-cho-Brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-brazil-vs-costa-rica-binh-luan-brazil-vs-costa-rica-421-189305.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Costa Rica kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Coutinho v\u1edbi b\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc t\u1eadn ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"496","checkdouble":"189354"},{"date":"15:38 23/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 19h00 ng\u00e0y 23/6 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/ha-noi-vs-da-nang-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\